    "updated_at": "2026-04-02T09:14:12Z",
    "body": "This issue can be reproduced even without custom symbols/emojis by installing the Google Cloud CLI, as starship's `gcloud` module uses `symbol = '☁️ '` by default, where the cloud emoji is `U+2601 U+FE0F`",
